channel.title: Help needed!
channel.description:
I would like to inform you all that we want to start a whole new age of programming and coding. We will be hiring coder that are willing to help in the making of Project Rune. If you can tell me what position you are best at doing i will put you in it. [IMG]http://i281.photobucket.com/albums/kk239/purez_2008/projectrune.jpg[/img]
Pm me if you have any questions about the Project Rune.
Managers owner purez -
Adding shops and items killa man owner purez - - - - Making a all new special Client owner pruez - - Adding Minigames - - - Thinking of server npcs and object places owner pruez - -
I am definitely serious about this. Consider carefully Wink
to join go to http://projectrune.smfforfree4.com/ or pm me or reply telling me what job you are interested in.
